GoldenEye::

She went to the side entrance and transformed into her golden eagle 
mode.  She flew high into the sky, soaring upon the warm breeze.  She 
was quickly insane.  She had hoped for more than just watching the 
dust settle on the armory shelves.  She decided to see what else was 
out there.  She went over the mountains and headed across the 
ocean. "Who knows, with my dumb luck, I'll get caught in a hurricane 
and lost at sea.  Well, if I can get that lucky."
She stretched her wings out fully and passed over the lazy waves of 
the sea.  After for what seemed like hours, she thought she saw 
something on the horizen.  An island perhaps.  She headed for it and 
road the wind currents towards the island.
